{"tid":903970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人真係冇得救","createTime":"2018-11-16T03:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T10:17:23.000Z","uid":143499,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d206d743b7fcc7be54453c1e97edb4a503f61eea","tid":903970,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"我說我今日返學去到北角地鐵站，一出就見到兩個支那女人拖住兩隻幼蟲準備喺棵樹樓下屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我今日心情好就行埋去同佢講匪語， 就話洗手間喺維多利亞公園入面; 佢話唔知點去我直頭帶佢去到公廁面前，佢講咗佢謝謝然後我就去咗隔離搭小巴上寶馬山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母一上到車經過啱啱顆樹就已經見到佢哋攞條j出嚟痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你班死賤種搵唔到廁所隨地屙尿都算啦， 屌你我帶埋你去廁所門口你都要痾喺棵樹隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係賤撚過我隻狗，我隻狗鋪咗報紙兜佢都識入去屙尿啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年美國阻止蘇聯核平北京簡直係現代人類文明最失策嘅事"},{"pid":"f4c23d7cccaf98a82ddf7912a07cc1069e20f199","tid":903970,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"講錯咗係天后唔係北角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d993293ff9a217727b4c8569ec227e199103af7","tid":903970,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到今時今日仲想可以教化班生番<br />\n你都幾on9下"},{"pid":"8dc7c61861be6125cd27e77b617c6d9a33db757c","tid":903970,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d993293ff9a217727b4c8569ec227e199103af7","tid":903970,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到今時今日仲想可以教化班生番<br />\n你都幾on9下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"我冇諗過廁所喺佢面前都要我喺棵樹度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事關顆樹附近有好多小朋友喺度玩，你話佢阿喺啲有錢佬門口或者鋪頭門口就關我撚事啫"},{"pid":"d0aa6681f33ba11b33534adad3dbd0b2ed99b644","tid":903970,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"大中華撚仲有冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20f69821e50c952285e5a67f12f4abf82d57d16","tid":903970,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"你會唔會後知後覺咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b58ceea3c53876510dce14fa543b2ee56c014c5","tid":903970,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"淋花施肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a506071ec95467d89111a79ddf212602e57f7d0","tid":903970,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"支那生番無一個係無辜的"},{"pid":"a5a0579de6ab6ebb88510a341d76feef5c594feb","tid":903970,"uid":38516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"入到公廁冇棵樹喺度佢唔識屙呀！<br />\n就好似啲狗咁，你帶佢去尿兜去馬桶，佢未必識屙一樣，不過狗係可以教到佢識，但蝗係點教都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58915443b3f635e2de7f893225d51ea281cc4d1","tid":903970,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"真係狗黎咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5db14c64d514a9d297622960f23430e140e660","tid":903970,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b58915443b3f635e2de7f893225d51ea281cc4d1","tid":903970,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"真係狗黎咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"